skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: random number generator
des:
In a pinch? Need a random number right now? This is the app for you. Simply ask Alexa for a random number and you will get a number between 0 and 9 (inclusive).
Need to know how many shots to take? BAM!
Need to know how many rounds of rock/paper/scissors to declare a winner? DONE!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
